  "text": "Then we have a condition where at the end of the first 25,000-year period, I would say the I'm guessing that the guardians discovered that there was no harvest of either positive or negatively oriented entities. Tell me then what happened, what action was taken, etc. I am Ra. There was no action taken except to remain aware of the possibility of a calling for help or understanding among the entities of this density. The Confederation is concerned with the preservation of the conditions conducive to learning. This, for the most part, revolves about the primal distortion of free will.",
